    <item>
      <title>Docs: Persistent Volume Optimization</title>
      <link>/docs/pv/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/pv/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        

&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Describes persistent volume information and details provided by optimization strategy.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;view-persistent-volume&#34;&gt;View &lt;code&gt;Persistent Volume&lt;/code&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#view-persistent-volume&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;code&gt;Persistent Volume&lt;/code&gt; menu on the left menu bar to display the persistent volume page, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/pv/pv1_hu69d02f4bcdead23c6ad90ea3ae35308d_70820_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;291&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Persistent Volume
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The persistent volume page is divided into thress areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cluster selection area&lt;/strong&gt;: Used for select a cluster.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Query area&lt;/strong&gt;: Used for filtering persistent volume by name, persistent volume claim namespace and name, strategy name and so on.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;List area&lt;/strong&gt;: Displays persistent volume, persistent volume claim, strategy name, usage, latest update time and realted actions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;After select a cluster, the list area will display persistent volumes of the selected cluster scaned by &lt;strong&gt;Cluster Optimizer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;s optimization strategies, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/pv/pv2_hu414cce39b47732d4873579d4d1e5c8b7_141167_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;370&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Persistent Volume: cluster selected
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The list area is divided into five columns:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PV&lt;/strong&gt;: displays the PV name, region, capacity and creation time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Owner&lt;/strong&gt;: displays information about resource&amp;rsquo;s owner, such as department, group and user.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PVC&lt;/strong&gt;: displays the PVC namespace and name.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Usage&lt;/strong&gt;: displays the usage of PV. For &lt;code&gt;Unused PV&lt;/code&gt; strategy, the usage information is empty.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Action&lt;/strong&gt;: displays the actions on the persistent volume.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;delete-persistent-volume&#34;&gt;Delete persistent volume&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#delete-persistent-volume&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;code&gt;Delete&lt;/code&gt; in action column in the row with &lt;code&gt;Unused PV&lt;/code&gt; strategy name above, it will open the &lt;code&gt;Delete Persistent Volume&lt;/code&gt; dialog, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/pv/pv3_huab26b7ec4eb695da86a41436be4f5126_65855_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;323&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Persistent Volume: delete persistent volume dialog
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It shows instructions on deleting persistent volume carefully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;adjust-persistent-volume-size&#34;&gt;Adjust persistent volume size&lt;a class=&#34;td-heading-self-link&#34; href=&#34;#adjust-persistent-volume-size&#34; aria-label=&#34;Heading self-link&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Select  &lt;code&gt;Low Utilization PV&lt;/code&gt; strategy in &lt;code&gt;Strategy Name&lt;/code&gt; select box of &lt;strong&gt;Query area&lt;/strong&gt;, then click &lt;code&gt;Query&lt;/code&gt; button, it will display the persistent volume list, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/pv/pv4_huf2bd82cfe369e8058e0bad552d9ab492_146004_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;500&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Persistent Volume: after select `Low Utilization PV` strategy
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Click &lt;code&gt;Adjust&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;strong&gt;action&lt;/strong&gt; column, it will open the &lt;code&gt;Adjust Persistent Volume Size&lt;/code&gt; dialog, as shown below.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;card rounded p-2 td-post-card mb-4 mt-4&#34; style=&#34;max-width: 910px&#34;&gt;
&lt;img class=&#34;card-img-top&#34; src=&#34;/docs/pv/pv5_hu0f907de8ad41cc128b3c6d8d95db1bf0_95987_900x0_resize_catmullrom_3.png&#34; width=&#34;900&#34; height=&#34;417&#34;&gt;
&lt;figcaption class=&#34;card-body px-0 pt-2 pb-0&#34;&gt;
&lt;p class=&#34;card-text&#34;&gt;


Persistent Volume: adjust persistent volume size
&lt;small class=&#34;text-muted&#34;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;Wiseinf Inc.&lt;/small&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/figcaption&gt;
&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It shows steps on resizing a persistent volume carefully.&lt;/p&gt;

